<span id="Description"></span>
==Popis==

The [[Image:Sketcher_Create3PointArc.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_Create3PointArc|Sketcher Create3PointArc]] tool creates an arc from its endpoints and a point along the arc. {{Version|1.0}}: This is the same tool as [[Sketcher_CreateArc|Sketcher CreateArc]] but with a different initial mode.

==Usage==

See also: [[Sketcher_Workbench#Drawing_aids|Drawing aids]].

# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_Create3PointArc.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_Create3PointArc|Arc From 3 Points]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → Geometries → [[Image:Sketcher_Create3PointArc.svg|16px]] Arc From 3 Points}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|G}} then {{KEY|3}}, then {{KEY|A}}.
# For further steps see [[Sketcher CreateArc#Usage|Sketcher CreateArc]].


